{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's very interesting what our reaction to that was when that fellow-- who was a second cousin to my mother-- knocked on our door and told us those horrible stories in 1942, right?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did he tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, well, I mean-- as you know, they went through in 1942 what we went through in 1944 later on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were put in a cattle wagon and taken away, right, essentially.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he, he illegally crossed the Hungarian border and came to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he knocked on our door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember our reaction very, very clearly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We listened to him with almost disbelief, right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we realized we have to help the man, and we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he slept there for awhile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then again, the, the official decrees appeared because he was not the only one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And between you and I, we were very relieved when he eventually moved on after a few days, right?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was illegal to, you know, to hide illegal refugees of this type.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where did he go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Really, I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he eventually found his way to Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we, you know-- people are very egocentric human beings, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We satisfied our, our obligation by helping him temporarily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We gave him some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the fact is that we were relieved when he moved on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was no, no organized-- it's very hard to understand for you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because nowadays, such a thing cannot happen, thank God.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in that atmosphere, it was no room for, for a great deal of organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only people who had the resemblance of, of doing something in an organized way were the Zionists.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They have in a modest way.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
